<cl=A2A2A2>

The most controversial guild for outsiders is Steel Masters. The eastern philosophy of spirit and training in which Masers aquire fantastic dexterity are the main pastime in the guild. Members of this guild are not as warlike as other guilds that reject magic, but in critical situations they are capable of causing the enemy enormous damage using their secret skills: Whirlwind and Divine Wind. However, Steel Masters do not attack without good reason, but prefer protection in which they have reached perfection. Even without armor, they can protect themselves from both magical and military attacks using the Guild's secret, the protective state of Kamae, when they become practically invulnerable.
<br>
